{"tid":1855854,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［星宇航空］首航不足半個月三條航線有兩條因疫情暫停","createTime":"2020-02-01T09:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:21:21.000Z","uid":48124,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"588f91e7e2b47e447f634b84fc426ad6133787c5","tid":1855854,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"1月23號先係台北首航<br />\n本身有三部A321neo，飛去澳門、越南、檳城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n形象走中高端路線<br />\n點知.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200201/1635886.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200201%2F1635886.htm&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b54d3d55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200201/1635886.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情升溫，義大利昨日宣布禁止中港澳台航班入境，越南也跟進禁止。近期開航峴港航線的星宇航空因此受害，桃園機場公司指出，星宇航空今日飛往越南峴港的JX1701航班，都已關閉閘門準備滑行時，卻被通知越南拒接，該班機只好滑回機坪，另外目前華航CI783也在前往胡志明市路上，若仍在台灣航管區域內，恐怕也得返航。<br />\n<br />\n桃園機場航務處長陳志嘉證實，由於越南禁止台灣航班入境，導致今日下午原定3時20分自桃機起飛的星宇航空JX1701航班無法如時起飛，陳志嘉指出，當時飛機都已關閉閘門開始滑行，塔台卻臨時接到越南的航空指示，由於武漢肺炎疫情，拒絕所有來自中港澳台航班，該班機只好滑回機坪並取消。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/451289278571041/posts/1050956448604318/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F451289278571041%2Fposts%2F1050956448604318%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=0551abb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/451289278571041/posts/1050956448604318/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n= 最新公告 =<br />\n　<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒疫情影響，星宇航空澳門航線班機異動如下，亦可至班機動態查詢🔎 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2O3jPq3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2O3jPq3&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=2fad51a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2O3jPq3</a><br />\n　<br />\n1月30日起至3月28日止：<br />\n🖋 桃園-澳門 JX205、澳門-桃園 JX206 取消<br />\n2月16日起至3月28日止：<br />\n🖋 桃園-澳門 JX203、澳門-桃園 JX204 取消<br />\n　<br />\n星宇航空將協助持有上述航班機票之旅客，轉搭星宇航空同航線其他航班。<br />\n旅客若持有１月28日(含)前開票往返桃園-澳門機票，欲改票或退票。"},{"pid":"17e84df4375afc8253fd5957ca8c84b1dcb17375","tid":1855854,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"出師不利"},{"pid":"81238f1584827956ff7abb6cc2ccbfb50adb9192","tid":1855854,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"嘿嘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9005786bd6f81d14e7284838a3c087fe4ee5a46d","tid":1855854,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"Solomon Yue大力推薦 &quot;香港普選計劃&quot;<br />\n垃圾政府狗官狗奴才 冇民主政治就冇民生 冇民生就連命都冇!<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=e5d2e5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n差2萬快啲入去簽今曰2月1最後1日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺whatsapp group廣傳</span>"},{"pid":"fe8c40d5c9517f3d737b365115cd786b1bf45e98","tid":1855854,"uid":48124,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"本身見到佢d嘢都幾靚仲想試吓搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fdGKH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fdGKH7.jpg&h=f083e26e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WuzOpH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuzOpH8.jpg&h=fe45f2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0uKHuP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0uKHuP.jpg&h=5d4c5e81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsPR6Wv.jpg\" data